<file path="agentic/schemas/README.md">
 1: # agentic/schemas/
 2: 
 3: Schemas are grouped by pipeline stage. Each sub-folder contains JSON Schema definitions for the data structures used at that stage.
 4: 
 5: | Folder | Purpose |
 6: |---|---|
 7: | `figma/` | Figma extraction inputs — node bundles, normalized tree, semantic tree, normalization/mapping reports |
 8: | `html/` | HTML pipeline outputs — blueprint, validation report, asset manifest, alt policy, section manifest |
 9: | `webflow/` | Webflow-side structures — native build plan, section tasks, write audit log |
10: | `library/` | CSS contract and project library schemas |
11: | `component/` | Component registry, signature, and matching report schemas |
12: | `design-system/` | Design-system sync report schema |
13: | `workspace/` | Runtime workspace file schemas — meta, state, page structure, error log, etc. |
14: 
15: ## Schema ↔ Pipeline Stage Mapping
16: 
17: ```
18: Figma MCP extraction  →  figma/figma-node-bundle.schema.json
19: Figma normalization   →  figma/figma-normalized-tree.schema.json
20:                          figma/figma-normalization-report.schema.json
21: Semantic resolution   →  figma/figma-semantic-tree.schema.json
22:                          figma/missing-mapping-report.schema.json
23: HTML rendering        →  html/html-blueprint.schema.json
24:                          html/html-validation-report.schema.json
25: Asset policy          →  html/asset-manifest.schema.json
26:                          html/alt-policy.schema.json
27: Chunk slicing         →  html/section-manifest.schema.json
28: Webflow native ops    →  webflow/webflow-native-build-plan.schema.json
29:                          webflow/webflow-section-task.schema.json
30:                          webflow/webflow-write-audit-log.schema.json
31: ```
</file>

