<file path="agentic/specs/system/workspace-artifact-schemas.md">
 1: # Workspace Artifact Schemas
 2: 
 3: Runtime artifacts live under `workspace/` and are generated by the pipeline compiler. The schemas in `agentic/schemas/` define the expected shape.
 4: 
 5: ## Core Folders
 6: 
 7: - `workspace/figma/` — Stable figma node extraction bundles and normalized trees.
 8: - `workspace/semantic/` — Semantic IR trees.
 9: - `workspace/html/` — Generated local HTML files and blueprints.
10: - `workspace/html/chunks/` — HTML slices for sections.
11: - `workspace/webflow-native/` — Webflow branch build plans, task logs, and write audit logs.
12: - `workspace/reports/` — Design-system sync, component matching, and QA verification reports.
13: 
14: ## Core Files & Schemas
15: 
16: | File/Path | Producer | Purpose | Schema |
17: |---|---|---|---|
18: | `workspace/figma/figma.node-bundle.json` | operator | Persisted Figma raw extraction tree. | `agentic/schemas/figma-node-bundle.schema.json` |
19: | `workspace/figma/figma.normalized-tree.json` | compiler | Normalized Figma tree. | `agentic/schemas/figma-normalized-tree.schema.json` |
20: | `workspace/semantic/figma.semantic-tree.json` | compiler | Semantic role/tag IR tree. | `agentic/schemas/figma-semantic-tree.schema.json` |
21: | `workspace/html/page.blueprint.json` | architect | Logical page layout blueprint. | `agentic/schemas/html-blueprint.schema.json` |
22: | `workspace/html/page.html` | compiler | Rendered HTML source page. | (Raw HTML Output) |
23: | `workspace/html/asset-manifest.json` | compiler | Asset role & alt manifest. | `agentic/schemas/asset-manifest.schema.json` |
24: | `workspace/webflow-native/native-build-plan.json` | compiler | Serialized Webflow mutation plan. | `agentic/schemas/webflow-native-build-plan.schema.json` |
25: | `workspace/webflow-native/write-audit-log.jsonl` | operator | Transactional audit log of writes. | `agentic/schemas/webflow-write-audit-log.schema.json` |
</file>

<file path="scripts/gates/pipeline/validate_asset_policy.py">
 1: #!/usr/bin/env python3
 2: """Deterministic quality gate for Asset Alt policy conformance."""
 3: from __future__ import annotations
 4: 
 5: import json
 6: import sys
 7: from datetime import datetime, timezone
 8: from pathlib import Path
 9: from typing import Any
10: 
11: def load_json(path: Path) -> Any:
12:     if not path.exists():
13:         return {}
14:     return json.loads(path.read_text(encoding="utf-8"))
15: 
16: def validate_assets(root: Path) -> list[str]:
17:     failures = []
18:     manifest_path = root / "workspace" / "html" / "asset-manifest.json"
19:     rules_path = root / "agentic" / "rules" / "asset-alt.rules.yaml"
20: 
21:     if not manifest_path.exists():
22:         failures.append("Asset manifest file is missing.")
23:         return failures
24: 
25:     manifest = load_json(manifest_path)
26:     
27:     # Load rules
28:     import yaml
29:     rules = {}
30:     if rules_path.exists():
31:         try:
32:             rules = yaml.safe_load(rules_path.read_text(encoding="utf-8"))
33:         except Exception:
34:             rules = {}
35:     
36:     policy = rules.get("asset_alt_policy", {})
37:     forbidden_generics = set(policy.get("forbidden_generic_alts", ["image", "logo", "photo", "placeholder"]))
38: 
39:     assets = manifest.get("assets", [])
40:     for asset in assets:
41:         node_id = asset.get("figma_node_id", "unknown")
42:         role = asset.get("role", "informative")
43:         alt = asset.get("alt_text", "")
44:         aria_hidden = asset.get("aria_hidden", False)
45: 
46:         if role == "informative":
47:             if not alt.strip():
48:                 failures.append(f"Node {node_id}: Informative image is missing alt text.")
49:             elif alt.strip().lower() in forbidden_generics:
50:                 failures.append(f"Node {node_id}: Informative image uses forbidden generic alt text '{alt}'.")
51:         elif role == "decorative":
52:             if alt.strip() != "":
53:                 failures.append(f"Node {node_id}: Decorative image must have empty alt text.")
54:             if not aria_hidden:
55:                 failures.append(f"Node {node_id}: Decorative image must have aria_hidden set to true.")
56:         elif role == "functional":
57:             if not alt.strip():
58:                 failures.append(f"Node {node_id}: Functional asset (icon/button) must have an accessible label.")
59:             elif alt.strip().lower() in forbidden_generics:
60:                 failures.append(f"Node {node_id}: Functional asset uses forbidden generic alt text '{alt}'.")
61:         elif role == "complex":
62:             if not alt.strip():
63:                 failures.append(f"Node {node_id}: Complex asset must have long description or alt text.")
64: 
65:     success = len(failures) == 0
66: 
67:     report_payload = {
68:         "verified_at": datetime.now(timezone.utc).isoformat(),
69:         "total_assets_checked": len(assets),
70:         "failures_count": len(failures),
71:         "failures": failures,
72:         "success": success
73:     }
74: 
75:     report_path = root / "workspace" / "reports" / "asset-policy-report.json"
76:     report_path.parent.mkdir(parents=True, exist_ok=True)
77:     report_path.write_text(json.dumps(report_payload, indent=2, ensure_ascii=False), encoding="utf-8")
78: 
79:     return failures
80: 
81: def main() -> int:
82:     root = Path(__file__).resolve().parents[3]
83:     failures = validate_assets(root)
84:     if failures:
85:         print("asset-policy-gate: FAIL")
86:         for f in failures:
87:             print(f"  - {f}")
88:         return 1
89:     print("asset-policy-gate: PASS")
90:     return 0
91: 
92: if __name__ == "__main__":
93:     sys.exit(main())
</file>

