<file path="scripts/gates/README.md">
 1: # scripts/gates/
 2: 
 3: Validation gates for the HTML-first compiler pipeline.
 4: 
 5: ## Runner
 6: 
 7: ```cmd
 8: # Run all HTML-first compiler gates:
 9: python scripts\gates\run_quality_gate.py --profile html-first
10: 
11: # Run default/general validation:
12: python scripts\gates\run_quality_gate.py
13: ```
14: 
15: ## Pipeline Gates (per compiler stage)
16: 
17: | Script | Validates |
18: |---|---|
19: | `validate_css_contract.py` | Client-First Library Contract generated correctly |
20: | `validate_css_index.py` | CSS class/variable index files exist |
21: | `validate_figma_node_bundle.py` | Figma extraction output schema |
22: | `validate_figma_normalization.py` | Normalized tree — no blockers, success flag |
23: | `validate_design_system_sync.py` | Figma tokens match CSS contract variables |
24: | `validate_component_matching.py` | Component signature matching report |
25: | `validate_semantic_ir.py` | Semantic IR — confidence ≥ 0.60, missing classes = 0 |
26: | `validate_html_blueprint.py` | HTML blueprint — wrapper elements exist, no inline styles |
27: | `validate_asset_policy.py` | Asset manifest alt policy compliance |
28: | `validate_html_chunks.py` | Section chunks sliced correctly, manifest balanced |
29: | `validate_resolver_benchmark.py` | Benchmark: ≥95% tag accuracy, 0 invented classes, broken fixtures fail |
30: | `validate_native_build_plan.py` | Native build plan — safe branch, no destructive ops, contract classes only |
31: 
32: ## System Gates (structural/quality)
33: 
34: | Script | Validates |
35: |---|---|
36: | `validate_agentic_structure.py` | All required specs, rules, schemas, folders exist |
37: | `validate_workspace_artifacts.py` | Workspace JSON files schema compliance |
38: | `validate_archive_cleanup.py` | Old scripts archived, no active stale references |
39: | `validate_project_library.py` | Per-project Client-First library completeness |
