<file path="source-css/README.md">
1: # Source CSS
2: 
3: This directory contains the original Client-First CSS files used to generate the library contract:
4: - `normalize.css`: Normalization styling rules.
5: - `webflow.css`: Webflow native engine reserved classes.
6: - `client-first-v2-2.webflow.css`: The Finsweet Client-First V2.2 stylesheet containing all design tokens and utility classes.
7: 
8: The generated contract is the source of truth for all compiler operations.
</file>

